---
// Categories Section - Categorías de formación
---

<section id="categorias" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <!-- Título de la sección -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-pfc-black mb-4">
        Nuestras <span class="text-pfc-red">Categorías</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-pfc-gray max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Un plan de formación para cada edad
      </p>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-pfc-red mx-auto mt-6"></div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Grid de Categorías -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Categoría 1: Iniciación -->
      <div class="group bg-pfc-gray-light rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551958219-acbc608c6377?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
            srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551958219-acbc608c6377?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80 1200w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551958219-acbc608c6377?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80 800w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551958219-acbc608c6377?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80 600w"
            sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 30vw, (min-width: 768px) 45vw, 90vw"
            alt="Categoría Iniciación"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-pfc-black/80 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Iniciación</h3>
            <p class="text-pfc-red font-bold text-lg">4 - 6 años</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <span class="inline-block bg-pfc-red text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
              Años de nacimiento: 2019 - 2021
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-pfc-gray mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Primer contacto con el balón en un ambiente divertido y estimulante para despertar el amor por el deporte.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pfc-red mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Desarrollo de psicomotricidad</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pfc-red mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Juegos y actividades lúdicas</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pfc-red mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Socialización y diversión</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Categoría 2: Formación -->
      <div class="group bg-pfc-gray-light rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553778263-73a83bab9b0c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
            srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553778263-73a83bab9b0c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80 1200w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553778263-73a83bab9b0c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80 800w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553778263-73a83bab9b0c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80 600w"
            sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 30vw, (min-width: 768px) 45vw, 90vw"
            alt="Categoría Formación"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-pfc-black/80 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Formación</h3>
            <p class="text-pfc-red font-bold text-lg">7 - 9 años</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <span class="inline-block bg-pfc-red text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
              Años de nacimiento: 2016 - 2018
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-pfc-gray mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Aprendizaje de fundamentos técnicos, coordinación y comprensión del juego desde los valores colectivos.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pfc-red mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Fundamentos técnicos del fútbol</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pfc-red mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Reglas básicas del juego</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pfc-red mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Trabajo en equipo básico</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Categoría 3: Desarrollo -->
      <div class="group bg-pfc-gray-light rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487466365202-1afdb86c764e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
            srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487466365202-1afdb86c764e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80 1200w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487466365202-1afdb86c764e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80 800w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487466365202-1afdb86c764e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80 600w"
            sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 30vw, (min-width: 768px) 45vw, 90vw"
            alt="Categoría Desarrollo"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-pfc-black/80 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Desarrollo</h3>
            <p class="text-pfc-red font-bold text-lg">10 - 12 años</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <span class="inline-block bg-pfc-red text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
              Años de nacimiento: 2014 - 2015
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-pfc-gray mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Perfeccionamiento técnico-táctico, hábitos de autocuidado y participación activa en competencias.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pfc-red mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Técnica avanzada y táctica</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pfc-red mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Juego colectivo y estrategia</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pfc-red mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm">Preparación para competencias</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- CTA debajo de las categorías -->
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <p class="text-lg text-pfc-gray mb-6">
        ¿No sabes en qué categoría inscribir a tu hijo? ¡Contáctanos y te asesoramos!
      </p>
      <a 
        href="https://wa.me/573025150090?text=Hola,%20necesito%20asesor%C3%ADa%20para%20saber%20en%20qu%C3%A9%20categor%C3%ADa%20inscribir%20a%20mi%20hijo." 
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-pfc-black text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-gray-800 transition-all hover:scale-105"
      >
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413Z"/>
        </svg>
        Solicitar asesoría
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

